  "instructions": [
    "1. In a large bowl, combine chopped makrut leaves, fresh mint leaves, sliced bliss, and thinly sliced red onion.",
    "2. In a small bowl, whisk together lime juice, coconut oil, and honey until well combined.",
    "3. Pour the dressing over the salad and toss to coat.",
    "4. Sprinkle chopped cilantro over the top of the salad.",
    "5. Season with salt to taste.",
    "6. Cover and refrigerate for at least 30 minutes to allow the flavors to meld.",
    "7. Serve chilled and enjoy!"
